4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The sum-product algorithm used in the proposed CEO decoder is a well-known algorithm in data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The soft estimator used in the CEO decoder can be seen as a machine learning technique.
